data.description: Indulge in the epitome of opulent living at 12900 Cedar Springs Rd. nestled within the prestigious Quail Creek Golf Community in North Oklahoma City. This grand abode exemplifies elegance and refinement, meticulously maintained to ensure a timeless allure that captivates at every turn. Step into a world of luxury as you enter this spacious residence, boasting four generously sized bedrooms and 3.5 baths. Ascend the staircase to discover an enchanting bonus room that offers endless possibilities for customization. The heart of this home is a magnificent living room adorned with soaring ceilings, radiant wooden beams, and expertly crafted built-ins that complement the grand stone fireplace. Sunlight pours in through expansive doors that seamlessly connect the indoors with the outdoors, illuminating the rich architectural details and lavish finishes. Prepare culinary masterpieces in a gourmet kitchen that showcases modernity and functionality with stainless steel appliances, including a six-burner cooktop and sumptuous granite countertops. This culinary haven is heaven for any aspiring chef. The sprawling owner's suite is a sanctuary of sophistication, featuring a substantial walk-in closet and an impeccably updated bathroom replete with a spacious shower and double vanities. Every inch of this room whispers indulgence. Step outside to an enchanting outdoor living area that overlooks a stunning pool, perfect for Oklahoma summers. This residence has undergone a complete transformation, boasting a full renovation that marries classic charm with modern convenience. It awaits a discerning family to bask in its splendor, just in time for the holidays. Welcome home to 12900 Cedar Springs Rd., where every corner radiates prestige, and every detail exudes elegance. Experience the height of luxury living in North Oklahoma City. Your dream home awaits.
